{"tid":97387,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump帶挈《1984》小說爆紅 書商加印應市","createTime":"2017-01-27T15:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T12:23:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c92ce04af831009ea3225a6150be3929fb2f1c6","tid":97387,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:19:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>川普另類事實爆紅 書商搶印1984</strong><br />\n<br />\n2017-01-26 12:02中央社 <br />\n紐約25日綜合外電報導<br />\n<br />\n由於美國總統川普政府掀起的「另類事實」風波，作家喬治‧歐威爾（George Orwell）的小說「1984」不但數十年後再版，<strong>更躍居美國暢銷書排行榜。</strong><br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，這本1949年首度發行的名著，描述狡詐的「老大哥」政府監視自己的人民，強迫他們接受「雙重思想」，或要他們同時接受相互矛盾的事實。<br />\n<br />\n白宮資深顧問康威（Kellyanne Conway）日前上美國國家廣播公司（NBC）週日政論節日「會晤新聞界」（Meet the Press），<span style=\"color: red;\">談論川普就職典禮觀禮人數時，使用「另類事實」一詞，讓1984頓時爆紅。</span><br />\n<br />\n若干評論家譴責康威的言論根本是「歐威爾主義」徹底展現。<br />\n<br />\n腦筋動得很快的出版商Signet Classics看到1984再掀熱潮，隨即發表聲明本週已下單再版7萬5000本，公司發言人昨晚更告訴美國有線電視新聞網（CNN），這樣的再版數量較一般來得多。<br />\n<br />\n曾矢言「反抗」川普移民與其他議題政策的美國民權聯盟（American Civil Liberties Union）西維吉尼亞分部則推文，他們已經選了1984作為本月讀書會的讀本。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10764/2253716?from=udn-relatednews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10764%2F2253716%3Ffrom%3Dudn-relatednews_ch2&d=nJdRGjnwq7hW3p2pQmlAyqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=0633d319\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10764/2253716?from=udn-relatednews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"71de1d3c246466d6cb7f46101d749d4d1d93486e","tid":97387,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536f1f689bbb702c3829f0903709ed4d06039377","tid":97387,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14486f7d53f8258b00b80c6e85437d1d9854bf8d","tid":97387,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc16d8ebf9e69b87b15d30907fb1bf47070b16d6","tid":97387,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.whale.to/a/4556551681_29d93f9eb5_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.whale.to%2Fa%2F4556551681_29d93f9eb5_z.jpg&h=35d3e40c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3380f732c5ffea6aaa1a1277b8d2e19c02c7bfe","tid":97387,"uid":16344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:02:29.000Z","msg":"做得好，美國必須消滅共產政權，核㓕支那"},{"pid":"626822e832f48554a0ebaa8cd482ab1b83bfa518","tid":97387,"uid":25316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:18:18.000Z","msg":"Big brother is watching you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cc9cb8bd663de4b9d8e42f6e6deb847470ff8f","tid":97387,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"on撚9，希拉蕊奧巴馬唔會監控？"},{"pid":"38747745b0aeff80a1841490a5c71299b1b13f76","tid":97387,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on撚9，希拉蕊奧巴馬唔會監控？</blockquote><br />\n都唔係講緊監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2658a94cb8975ddd6319bc85593246a83ed4edd0","tid":97387,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}